text: Selena Gomez Watched the Super Bowl With a Bunch of Couples -- But Where Was The Weeknd? by Jennifer Drysdale 7:16   Photo: Instagram Selena Gomez is missing her new boo! The 24-year-old singer found herself playing 3rd wheel on Super Bowl Sunday, watching the game with a room full of couples. Gomez took to Instagram Stories to share a snap of her viewing party, with The Weeknd nowhere to be found. Selena Gomez and friends watching the #SuperBowl via Instagram Stories pic.twitter.com/181ouBpL53 â€” Selena Gomez News (@SelenaHQ) February 6, 2017 Without updates on his own social media accounts, it seems the "Starboy" singer missed out on the big game -- including Justin Bieber's Super Bowl commercial.   Says The Weeknd's Music Is 'Wack' Following Selena Gomez Romance Rumors Absence clearly makes the heart grow fonder for Gomez and The Weeknd, who recently spent a PDA-filled week together in Venice, Italy. The new couple were first spotted smooching last month during a night out in Los Angeles -- just two months after The Weeknd split from Bella Hadid -- but have definitely have taken their romance to the next level.
